  "legend": "",
  "role": "Other",
  "loadout": "<b>This model is equipped with:</b> 2 heavy flamers; 2 lascannons; siege melta array; skyreaper battery; armoured tracks.",
  "transport": "This model has a transport capacity of 45 <span class=\"tooltip00327\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00327\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00327\"><span class=\"kwb\">DEATH</span> <span class=\"kwb\">GUARD</span> <span class=\"kwb\">INFANTRY</span></span> models. Each <span class=\"tooltip00324\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00324\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00324\"><span class=\"kwb\">JUMP</span> <span class=\"kwb\">PACK</span></span>, <span class=\"tooltip00279\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00279\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00279\"><span class=\"kwb\">WULFEN</span></span>, <span class=\"tooltip00325\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00325\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00325\"><span class=\"kwb\">GRAVIS</span></span>, <span class=\"kwb kwbo\">POSSESSED</span> or <span class=\"tooltip00262\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00262\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00262\"><span class=\"kwb\">TERMINATOR</span></span> model takes up the space of 2 models and each <span class=\"tooltip00326\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00326\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00326\"><span class=\"kwb\">CENTURION</span></span> or <span class=\"kwb kwbo\">OBLITERATOR</span> model takes up the space of 3 models. This model can also transport up to 2 <span class=\"tooltip00263\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00263\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00263\"><span class=\"kwb\">DREADNOUGHT</span></span> or <span class=\"kwb kwbo\">HELBRUTE</span> models (these models take up the space of a number of models equal to their Wounds characteristic e.g. A <span class=\"tooltip00320\" data-tooltip-content=\"#tooltip_content00320\" data-tooltip-anchor=\"#tooltip_content00320\"><span class=\"kwb\">DREADNOUGHT</span></span> with a Wounds characteristic of 8 would take up the space of 8 models).",
  "virtual": false,
